### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### Create New User - Bob
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "age": 35
}


### Update User by ID (Replace with actual MongoDB ObjectId)
