{ "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Bob",
  "age": 40
}

### Delete User by ID (Replace with actual MongoDB ObjectId)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/2

### Search Users - Case insensitive
GET http://localhost:3000/search?name=John


### Get Single User by ID (Replace with actual MongoDB ObjectId)
